非常感谢exg社区的各位为测试本图所做出的贡献！祝你玩得开心！！！.Translation: Thank you very much to everyone in the exg community for their contributions to testing this map! Have fun!!!

boss出现了！我们只有两分钟的时间！！！快击败他！！.Translation: The boss has appeared! We only have 120 seconds to defeat him!!! Hurry!!

boss死了！！僵尸出笼！有序撤退！！！！.Translation: The boss is dead!! Zombies are emerging! Retreat in an orderly fashion!!!!

我们在更衣室找到了一张设施员工林燕的工作牌！或许他能带领我们在这个地方畅通无阻！.Translation: We found a work badge of facility staff Lin Yan in the changing room! Perhaps he can help us navigate this place smoothly!

成功了！门开始移动了！！林燕不愧是权王！！！.Translation: Success! The door is starting to move!! Lin Yan truly is the king of power!!!

灭火器已经被拿到！坚持住！我们需要把通风管道的火焰灭掉才能通过！.Translation: The fire extinguisher has been obtained! Hold on! We need to extinguish the flames in the ventilation duct to pass!

灭火器已经使用！火焰已经熄灭！快撤退！.Translation: The fire extinguisher has been used! The flames are out! Retreat quickly!

坚持住！电梯还有30s才能启动！.Translation: Hold on! The elevator will start in 30 seconds!

坚持住！10秒后电梯上升！.Translation: Hold on! The elevator will rise in 10 seconds!

火焰已经被灭火器熄灭！.Translation: The flames have been extinguished by the fire extinguisher!

梯子将在15s后解锁！.Translation: The ladder will unlock in 15 seconds!

梯子将在5s后解锁！.Translation: The ladder will unlock in 5 seconds!

电梯将在30s后上升！.Translation: The elevator will rise in 30 seconds!

电梯将在5s后上升！.Translation: The elevator will rise in 5 seconds!

消防系统将在30秒后启动！.Translation: The fire suppression system will activate in 30 seconds!

坚持住！10秒后火焰熄灭！.Translation: Hold on! The flames will be extinguished in 10 seconds!

奶神器已经被拾取！.Translation: The Heal Artifact has been picked up!

奶神器已使用！！冷却时间60s！.Translation: Heal Artifact has been used!! Cooldown time 60 seconds!!

秒杀神器已经被拾取！120s冷却！秒杀周围一定范围内的僵尸！.Translation: The One-Hit Artifact has been picked up! 120 seconds cooldown! Instantly kills zombies within a certain range!
